      "justification_wrong": "Structured deposits characterize placement (initial entry), while asset purchases and commingling represent integration (reintroducing laundered funds into legitimate economy). Layering specifically employs complex, rapid movement across multiple accounts and jurisdictions to obscure origins before final integration per ACFE taxonomy.",
