      "justification_wrong": "Placement introduces illicit cash into financial systems initially. Integration returns laundered funds to legitimate use. Structuring specifically involves breaking transactions below reporting thresholds (typically $10,000). The described pattern of large transfers through multiple jurisdictions represents sophisticated layering per ACFE money laundering identification framework, not other stages.",
